headline.print_headline: Kahne Knows He's Got to Step It Up for Hendrick
headline.main: Kahne Knows He's Got to Step It Up for Hendrick

lead_paragraph: Hendrick Motorsports likes things neat and clean and organized. NASCAR's top team works hard to avoid drama, and its way of doing business is a huge part of the organization's success.
